gh  wk low  full description goldcorp inc goldcorp incorporated on december   is a gold producer engaged in the operation exploration development and acquisition of precious metal properties in canada the united states mexico and central and south america the companys segments include red lake gold mines ontario partnership red lake goldcorp canada ltdgoldcorp inc porcupine goldcorp canada ltdgoldcorp inc musselwhite les mines opinaca ltee eleonore kaminak gold corporation kaminak minera penasquito sa de cv and camino rojo sa de cv penasquito oroplata sa cerro negro minera alumbrera limited alumbrera pueblo viejo dominicana corporation pueblo viejo and nuevaunion spa nuevaunion the companys principal producing mining properties consist of the eleonore musselwhite porcupine and red lake mines in canada the penasquito mine in mexico the cerro negro mine in argentina and the pueblo viejo mine in the dominican republic the companys principal product is gold dore with the refined gold bullion sold primarily in the london spot marketthe companys red lake project is located approximately  kilometers northwest of dryden ontario the companys mining operation covers approximately  hectares and is accessible by highway  which heads north from the transcanada highway at red lake there are two projects cochenour and hg young the companys eleonore project is located in goldproducing district the northeast corner of the opinaca reservoir in the james bay region of quebec canada eleonore is located within the contact zone between the la grande and opinaca subprovinces the companys porcupine project is located in timmins ontario its porcupine project consists of four mining operations hoyle pond dome underground and the hollinger open pit all of which feed the dome processing facilitythe companys musselwhite mine is a flyinflyout operation on the southern shore of opapimiskan lake in northwestern ontario canada  kilometers north of thunder bay the musselwhite property consists of a combination of leases and mining claim units covering a total area of approximately  hectares entirely on first nations land the companys borden project located near chapleau in ontario is approximately  kilometers west of goldcorps porcupine mine the companys cochenour project is located five kilometers west of the companys operation red lake gold mines and approximately  kilometers northwest of dryden ontario the cochenour project is situated in the eastern part of the red lake greenstone belt in the birchuchi lake subprovince of the superior province within the core of the canadian shieldthe companys penasquito mine is a gold producer consisting of two open pits penasco and chile colorado containing gold silver lead and zinc the penasquito mine is located in the northeastern part of the state of zacatecas in northcentral mexico  kilometers east of the town of mazapil the companys los filos operation consists el bermejal and one underground mine the companys el sauzal project is located in chihuahua state mexico el sauzal mine the companys marlin mine is in the western highlands of guatemala in the municipality of san miguel ixtahuacan  kilometers westsouthwest of the town of huehuetenango approximately  kilometers northwest of guatemala citythe companys alumbrera project is located near belen argentina in catamarca province approximately  kilometers northwest of buenos aires the companys pueblo viejo project is located in the dominican republic approximately  kilometers northwest of the capital city of santo domingo the companys cerro negro project is located on the patagonian plains in the southern argentinean province of santa cruz at an elevation of approximately  meters above sea level the companys san martin project is located in central honduras approximately  kilometers north of the capital city of tegucigalpa san martin is situated the upper slopes of the valley of siria in the municipality of san ignacio the companys camino rojo goldsilver project is located  kilometers southeast of the penasquito mine in the state of zacatecas in northcentral mexico the nuevaunion project includes the el morro goldcopper deposit and the relincho coppermolybdenum deposit its coffee project is a hosted hydrothermal deposit located approximately  kilometers south of the city of dawson yukon » full overview of gg company address goldcorp inc park place  burrard st suitevancouver   bc   vc x p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation ian telfer  david garofalo  beverley briscoe  russell ball  todd white  » more officers  directors goldcorp inc news canadian miner goldcorp may sell royalties portfolio jul   canada stockstsx rises as energy shares gain cenovus jumps jul   canadas goldcorp earnings beat analyst estimates cfo to leave jul   update canadas goldcorp earnings beat analyst estimates cfo to leave jul   goldcorp posts quarterly profit as costs fall cfo to leave jul   » more gg news related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialsgold flashratings  about us facebook autocomplete demo post a rating  month price target   trending sign up log in flashratings  all research for my stocks the most comprehensive equity research coverage available online never miss a single piece of research upgrade downgrade or target price change by any analyst firm on any stock equity research by professional analysts  especially their rationales more than their forecasts  contains far more interesting and important information about the actual fundamentals of the traded companies than can be gathered from conventional news reports our mission is to unlock access to valuable research on stocks for all retail investors professionals institutions take advantage of our costeffective subscriptions to have flashratingss comprehensive realtime feed delivered into your intranet and trading floor platforms institutional subscriptions websites become a content licensing partner and display flashratingss popular news feed on your w