projects and we need a range of professionals to sustain our growth from engineering geology and metallurgy to financial and management staff build your success while we build ours apply now skilled  technical you have expertise skills and a dedication to excellence we have major projects under development with challenges that will put you to the test and give you the opportunity to make more of your career than you’d have thought possible you’ll appreciate our focus on safety teamwork and our commitment to supporting your career development apply now students  new grads you’re looking for somewhere to start your career—somewhere you can learn from the best in the industry and build a track record join goldcorp and you can participate in major projects across the americas—work with some of the most respected team leaders and technical experts—and employ the most advanced technologies for someone with skills intelligence and ambition the opportunities at goldcorp are unmatched apply now goldcorp is a company thats going to be around for a long time it has opportunities that no other company has available its a great place to learn if you want to be the best and work with the best i suggest that you contact goldcorp don burke   didn’t find what you were looking for if you do not find a job that matches your interests please click here to submit your employment profile and sign up for job alerts investors links financial highlights financial reports stock information events and webcasts news presentations reserves  resources interactive analyst center about us why goldcorp our culture board management governance  policies awards  recognition membership  commitments corporate directory careers opportunities inside goldcorp students  new grads tsx g     volume  july   nyse gg     volume  july   gold us     volume july   subscribe  contact  sitemap  legal powered by q inc  goldcorp inc  about us  corporate directory tsx g     volume  july   nyse gg     volume  july   gold